oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Karl Shiflett and Big Country Show at Station Inn

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and blue on white) announcing the Karl Shiflett and Big Country Show album release for "Worries on My Mind" at the Station Inn on October 30. Poster features a woodcut of a jockey riding a horse and the phrase "I'm goin', Are you?"
